<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> rāja</hi>nā<hi rend="grantha">rā</hi>yaṇaṉ campuva<hi rend="grantha">rāja</hi>rkku yā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇṭu <num value="12"><g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num> vatu poṉṉūr maṇṇaipoṉṉāṇṭai
